    { "text": "理解同底数幂乘法法则的推导过程", "isKeyPoint": true },
    { "text": "掌握同底数幂的乘法法则：$a^m \\cdot a^n = a^{m+n}$", "isKeyPoint": true },
    { "text": "能运用法则进行同底数幂的乘法运算", "isKeyPoint": true },
    { "text": "了解法则可以推广到多个同底数幂相乘的情况", "isKeyPoint": false },
    { "text": "体会从特殊到一般的数学思想方法", "isKeyPoint": false }
  ],
  "knowledge": [
    {
      "title": "同底数幂乘法法则",
      "defaultExpanded": true,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "**同底数幂的乘法法则**：同底数幂相乘，底数不变，指数相加。即：$a^m \\cdot a^n = a^{m+n}$（$m$、$n$ 为正整数）。"
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "variant": "tip",
          "title": "推导过程",
          "content": "$a^m \\cdot a^n = \\underbrace{a \\cdot a \\cdots a}_{m \\text{ 个}} \\cdot \\underbrace{a \\cdot a \\cdots a}_{n \\text{ 个}} = \\underbrace{a \\cdot a \\cdots a}_{m+n \\text{ 个}} = a^{m+n}$"
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "variant": "warning",
          "title": "易错提醒",
          "content": "底数必须相同才能使用此法则！如 $a^2 \\cdot b^3$ 不能写成 $a^{2+3}$，因为底数不同，不能合并。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "法则的推广",
      "defaultExpanded": true,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "同底数幂的乘法法则可以推广到多个同底数幂相乘的情况：$a^m \\cdot a^n \\cdot a^p = a^{m+n+p}$。"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "一般地，$n$ 个同底数幂相乘：$a^{m_1} \\cdot a^{m_2} \\cdots a^{m_n} = a^{m_1+m_2+\\cdots+m_n}$。"
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "variant": "note",
          "title": "注意",
          "content": "当指数为字母时，法则同样适用。例如 $a^x \\cdot a^y = a^{x+y}$（$x$、$y$ 为正整数）。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "运算注意事项",
      "defaultExpanded": false,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "使用同底数幂乘法法则时，需要注意以下几点："
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            "底数相同，指数相加，底数不变",
            "底数不同时，不能使用此法则",
            "多个同底数幂相乘，指数全部相加",
            "运算结果仍为幂的形式"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "variant": "mnemonic",
          "title": "记忆口诀",
          "content": "同底数幂把乘算，底数不变指数加。多个相乘也一样，指数全加别犯傻。"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "examples": [
    {
      "title": "例1：基本运算",
      "problem": [
        { "type": "paragraph", "content": "计算：(1) $a^3 \\cdot a^4$；(2) $x^2 \\cdot x^5 \\cdot x^3$。" }
      ],
      "solution": [
        { "type": "paragraph", "content": "(1) $a^3 \\cdot a^4 = a^{3+4} = a^7$" },
        { "type": "paragraph", "content": "(2) $x^2 \\cdot x^5 \\cdot x^3 = x^{2+5+3} = x^{10}$" }
      ],
      "answer": "(1) $a^7$；(2) $x^{10}$"
    },
    {
      "title": "例2：含系数的运算",
      "problem": [
        { "type": "paragraph", "content": "计算：$3x^2 \\cdot 5x^3$。" }
      ],
      "solution": [
        { "type": "paragraph", "content": "$3x^2 \\cdot 5x^3 = (3 \\times 5)(x^2 \\cdot x^3) = 15x^{2+3} = 15x^5$" }
      ],
      "answer": "$15x^5$"
    }
  ],
  "summary": [
    {
      "text": "同底数幂的乘法法则",
      "children": [
        { "text": "$a^m \\cdot a^n = a^{m+n}$（底数不变，指数相加）" },
        { "text": "推广：$a^{m_1} \\cdot a^{m_2} \\cdots a^{m_n} = a^{m_1+m_2+\\cdots+m_n}$" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "使用条件",
      "children": [
        { "text": "底数必须相同" },
        { "text": "指数为正整数" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "常见错误",
      "children": [
        { "text": "底数不同不能直接用法则" },
        { "text": "不能把指数相乘" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}